# Route gettext catalogs through the `po-clean` clean filter so source-line
# shifts and the POT-Creation-Date header never surface as phantom diffs/
# conflicts. The filter is registered in local git config by
# scripts/install-hooks.sh — run that once per clone. If it is not registered
# git treats `po-clean` as a no-op, so this line is harmless on its own.
*.po  filter=po-clean
*.pot filter=po-clean
